https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install

Who can attend? 👧👧🏻👧🏼👧🏽👧🏾👧🏿
Flutter Study Jam is best suited for those just getting started with mobile app development or those with programming experience on other mobile app frameworks or anyone with some programming skills and wants to expand his/her knowledge and is keen to learn more 🔥🤩

So are you any of those mentioned above?

Agenda:

6:00-7:00 >> Introduction to the Magic of Flutter

7:00-7:15 >> Install Flutter

7:15-8:15 >> Flutter Interact Keynote

8:15-9:15 >> DartPad Playthings Activity

So what are you waiting for? Come join us for a surprise at the end 🚀
